Teltoli's ears pricked up, and she heard what sounded like talking, 
the these trees made it hard to define. Running quickly up to within 
a few meters of it, she saw that some bot with a scythe was attacking 
an obviously innocent bot, whom she couldn't get a good glance at.

Sabre fluttered into the trees, and she let out a resounding panther 
shriek, before transforming and dodging up to the bot with the 
scythe, pointing her poison dart point blank at it's head.

"Law of the jungle, idiot, eat or be eaten. Or in this case.. slag or 
be slagged. What do you think you're doing?" She said in a deathly 
calm voice.
